At the San Francisco Department of Public Health (DPH) (SFDPH) our mission is to protect and promote health and well-being for all in San Francisco. Our vision is making San Francisco the healthiest place on earth.
SFDPH consists of central administration and two divisions:
 Population Health Division (PHD)  San Francisco Health Network (SFHN)  The most recent SFDPH Organization Chart is available here.
